  body
    #nav
      .container
        #logo WorkQuest
        .nav-right
          #nav-stats
            span.username Jonny the Destroyer
            span.level 17

    .row.big-container
      .six.columns.user-stats
        .four.columns
          img(src='images/ascended.jpg')
        .eight.columns
          h2 Jonny Balls
          h5 Ascended One
          p Your levels of productivity are typically only reached after years of contemplation in tibetan monastaries. Mortals peform pilgramage yearly in order to worship at your feet. They watch in wonder as you code at near super-human speeds, your hands dancing across the keys, creating software of breathtaking beauty.
      .six.columns
        table.u-full-width
          thead
            tr
              th Name
              th Level
          tbody
            tr
              td Siokhan
              td 3
            tr
              td Pedro Santos de Mendonca
              td 2

    .row.tasklists
      .four.columns.tasklist
        .tasktitle Available
        ul.tasks
          li Make templates
          li Make login
          li Download assets
